<section class="static-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header"><h1>{{ page.title | default: 'Frequently Asked Questions' }}</h1></div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question active" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>Do whitening strips work?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer open">
          <p>Yes — our teeth whitening strips deliver an enamel-safe whitening gel directly to your teeth to break down stains. They are designed to give a visibly whiter smile after a single 7-day treatment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>How quickly will I see results?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Most people notice a difference within 3–5 days, with optimal results after the full 7-day treatment of consistent daily use.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>Are the whitening strips safe for sensitive teeth?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. Our strips use a balanced, enamel-safe formula with protective compounds designed to minimize sensitivity. If you have dental concerns, please review our Product Safety page or consult your dentist first.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>How do I use the whitening strips?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Peel and press one strip onto your upper teeth and one onto your lower teeth, leave for 30 minutes, then remove and rinse. Use once daily for 7 days. Avoid eating or drinking while wearing the strips.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>How long do results last?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Results typically last 6–12 months with good oral care. Occasional touch-up treatments help maintain your brighter smile.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>How much does shipping cost and how long does it take?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Shipping is free worldwide on every order. Your whitening strips typically arrive within 6–10 days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>What is your refund policy?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We offer a 7-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied, email us within 7 days of receiving your order and we'll make it right. See our <a href="/pages/refund-policy">Refund Policy</a> for details.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>How can I contact you?</span>
          <svg class="faq-toggle" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:camilasousa@duck.com">camilasousa@duck.com</a> or call <a href="tel:920715535">920715535</a>. We reply within 24–48 hours, Monday to Friday.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
